Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: The Baddies
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cstzb5
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 4 Sep 2017
Jasmin Geljo was one of the most famous actors in the former Yugoslavia and Luc Bendza grew up in Gabon a massive fan of martial arts films. Both found themselves living a long way from home and with careers playing the baddies in movies. Photo: Luz Bendza performing Kung Fu. Credit: ‘Taken from the documentary The African Who Wanted to Fly’ Show less